<plot>This film explores the history of editorial cartoons in Canadian history. Throughout most of the history of this country, there have been cartoonists who are able and willing to poke fun at the events and figures of life that deserve it. This film interviews several prominent talents in this field and explores the impact that these cartoons have had on Canadian history.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?564084</url></doc>
